[h2 id=BizhawkAndSoftResets 
	"Bizhawk and Soft Resets
	$LF
]h2
[div class=p 
	"The Gens emulator does not have the soft reset feature meaning that I have to complete every zone including the cutscenes, even the long ones. Converting to Bizhawk fixed this issue and saved around 20 seconds of my final Gens run with Knuckles. The run lasted for 20:36.65 and it was cut down to 20:17.57 thanks to the 3 soft resets that were used at the end of Launch Base, Mushroom Hill and Flying Battery. These soft resets are used to skip the long cutscenes which were at least 7+ seconds long. They are implemented at the frames where the time bonus hits 0 so that the run counts the frames with the time bonus counting down.
	$LF
]div
